name: EYN - European Youth Network
goal:
Education and training organisation, active in education and training of young people, research in the fields of: economics, process of making laws, urban development, management of media.

EYN - European Youth Network is located in Treviso (TV), in the North-East of Italy, and is searching for partenerships with other EU no-profit organisations (from EU countries), private sector and public sector.
interests: Culture, Development, Education, Employment and Social Affairs, Enlargement, External Relations, General and Institutional Affairs, Home Affairs, Humanitarian Aid, Internal Market, Justice and Fundamental Rights, Regional Policy, Sport, Trans-European Networks, Transport, Youth
euInitiatives: Research, education, training and skills, economics, management of media, urban and sustainable development.
